===[[Pokémon Trading Card Game Pocket]]===
{{main|Misty (Genetic Apex 220)}}
Misty makes an appearance as a {{TCG|Supporter}} card in [[Pokémon Trading Card Game Pocket]]'s first expansion, {{TCGP|Genetic Apex}}. When the player plays this card, they pick one of their {{TCG|Water}} Pokémon in play and flip a {{TCG|coin}} until they get tails; for each heads flipped, they take a {{TCG|Water}} {{TCG|Energy}} from the Energy Zone and attach it to the selected Pokémon.

